    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MATURE CONTENT WARNING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our game is a zombie shooting experience that features intense combat scenarios, including depictions of violence against zombie enemies. Players will engage in action-packed gameplay involving weapons, blood effects, and graphic depictions of undead creatures. The game contains no sexual content or themes but does include elements of horror and gore, which may not be suitable for sensitive audiences. It does not depict or involve topics such as sexual assault, drug/alcohol abuse, or self-harm. The mature content is focused solely on the thrill of battling against zombie hordes in a survival setting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055580/extras/485ad7ab2876c75792aa5d9e93299a84.poster.avif?t=1771909625\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055580/extras/485ad7ab2876c75792aa5d9e93299a84.webm?t=1771909625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055580/extras/485ad7ab2876c75792aa5d9e93299a84.mp4?t=1771909625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dive into the apocalyptic world of <strong>Necroverse</strong>, where survival is just the beginning. In this adrenaline-pumping zombie shooter, face relentless hordes of the undead and rival players in <strong>Battle Royale Mode</strong>—an unforgiving test of strategy, skill, and sheer will to survive.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle Royale Mode: PvPvZ at Its Finest</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055580/extras/6aab854caf6197db1c1a224feca8bac6.poster.avif?t=1771909625\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055580/extras/6aab854caf6197db1c1a224feca8bac6.webm?t=1771909625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055580/extras/6aab854caf6197db1c1a224feca8bac6.mp4?t=1771909625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter an arena like no other, where the fight for survival pits you against both human adversaries and relentless waves of the undead. Compete to outlast everyone, battling the undead while strategically eliminating other players to claim ultimate victory.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055580/extras/e7f00cecabb422f77fec01d0666ac2be.poster.avif?t=1771909625\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055580/extras/e7f00cecabb422f77fec01d0666ac2be.webm?t=1771909625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055580/extras/e7f00cecabb422f77fec01d0666ac2be.mp4?t=1771909625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Will you emerge as the last one standing in the <strong>Necroverse</strong>?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every move counts, every shot matters. The question isn’t if you’ll survive the night—but how.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Download now and face the Necroverse.</strong></p>",
